title: Kropp Struktur Size Kalkylator
metaDescription: Gratis body frame size calculator - Determine if you have a small, medium, or large body frame using wrist circumference or elbow breadth.

form.title: Ange your information
form.methodHelp: Choose a method baserat på which measurement you can take most easily
form.wristHelp: Measure the circumference of your wrist just above the prominent wrist bone
form.elbowHelp: Extend your arm forward with palm up. Bend elbow to 90°. Measure the distance between the two prominent elbow bones
